    {"type":"text","id":"p5-title","x":70,"y":1240,"width":500,"height":30,"text":"PHASE 5 — CUSTOMER ACQUISITION","fontSize":24,"fontFamily":1,"textAlign":"left","verticalAlign":"middle","containerId":null,"originalText":"PHASE 5 — CUSTOMER ACQUISITION","autoResize":true,"lineHeight":1.25,"versionNonce":0,"isDeleted":false,"fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":2,"strokeStyle":"solid","roughness":1,"opacity":100,"angle":0,"strokeColor":"#1e1e1e","backgroundColor":"transparent","seed":51,"groupIds":[],"frameId":null,"boundElements":null,"updated":1,"link":null,"locked":false},
    {"type":"text","id":"p5-week","x":650,"y":1240,"width":180,"height":25,"text":"Weeks 8-16","fontSize":18,"fontFamily":1,"textAlign":"right","verticalAlign":"middle","containerId":null,"originalText":"Weeks 8-16","autoResize":true,"lineHeight":1.25,"versionNonce":0,"isDeleted":false,"fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":2,"strokeStyle":"solid","roughness":1,"opacity":60,"angle":0,"strokeColor":"#ef4444","backgroundColor":"transparent","seed":52,"groupIds":[],"frameId":null,"boundElements":null,"updated":1,"link":null,"locked":false},
    {"type":"text","id":"p5-items","x":80,"y":1278,"width":750,"height":200,"text":"1. Google Ads — \"Botox near me\", \"lip filler [city]\", \"med spa [city]\" (highest intent)\n2. Meta Ads — before/after content, seasonal promos (target women 25-55, HHI $75K+)\n3. Grand opening event (free consults, demo treatments, influencer invites, champagne)\n4. Referral program ($50 credit for referrer, $50 off for friend)\n5. Strategic partnerships (dermatologists, plastic surgeons, OBGYNs, gyms, salons)\n6. Influencer collaborations (gift treatments to local micro-influencers for content)\n7. Seasonal promotions (summer body prep, holiday glow-ups, wedding season, NYE)\n8. Community events & educational workshops (lunch & learn, skincare classes)","fontSize":16,"fontFamily":1,"textAlign":"left","verticalAlign":"top","containerId":null,"originalText":"1. Google Ads — \"Botox near me\", \"lip filler [city]\", \"med spa [city]\" (highest intent)\n2. Meta Ads — before/after content, seasonal promos (target women 25-55, HHI $75K+)\n3. Grand opening event (free consults, demo treatments, influencer invites, champagne)\n4. Referral program ($50 credit for referrer, $50 off for friend)\n5. Strategic partnerships (dermatologists, plastic surgeons, OBGYNs, gyms, salons)\n6. Influencer collaborations (gift treatments to local micro-influencers for content)\n7. Seasonal promotions (summer body prep, holiday glow-ups, wedding season, NYE)\n8. Community events & educational workshops (lunch & learn, skincare classes)","autoResize":true,"lineHeight":1.25,"versionNonce":0,"isDeleted":false,"fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":2,"strokeStyle":"solid","roughness":1,"opacity":85,"angle":0,"strokeColor":"#1e1e1e","backgroundColor":"transparent","seed":53,"groupIds":[],"frameId":null,"boundElements":null,"updated":1,"link":null,"locked":false},

