    {"type":"text","id":"p6-title","x":70,"y":1530,"width":600,"height":30,"text":"PHASE 6 — SCALE TO $50-100K/MONTH","fontSize":24,"fontFamily":1,"textAlign":"left","verticalAlign":"middle","containerId":null,"originalText":"PHASE 6 — SCALE TO $50-100K/MONTH","autoResize":true,"lineHeight":1.25,"versionNonce":0,"isDeleted":false,"fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":2,"strokeStyle":"solid","roughness":1,"opacity":100,"angle":0,"strokeColor":"#1e1e1e","backgroundColor":"transparent","seed":61,"groupIds":[],"frameId":null,"boundElements":null,"updated":1,"link":null,"locked":false},
    {"type":"text","id":"p6-week","x":650,"y":1530,"width":180,"height":25,"text":"Months 4-12","fontSize":18,"fontFamily":1,"textAlign":"right","verticalAlign":"middle","containerId":null,"originalText":"Months 4-12","autoResize":true,"lineHeight":1.25,"versionNonce":0,"isDeleted":false,"fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":2,"strokeStyle":"solid","roughness":1,"opacity":60,"angle":0,"strokeColor":"#f59e0b","backgroundColor":"transparent","seed":62,"groupIds":[],"frameId":null,"boundElements":null,"updated":1,"link":null,"locked":false},
    {"type":"text","id":"p6-math","x":80,"y":1565,"width":750,"height":25,"text":"Revenue math: 15-25 clients/day x $350 avg x 22 days = $115-192K/month","fontSize":16,"fontFamily":1,"textAlign":"left","verticalAlign":"middle","containerId":null,"originalText":"Revenue math: 15-25 clients/day x $350 avg x 22 days = $115-192K/month","autoResize":true,"lineHeight":1.25,"versionNonce":0,"isDeleted":false,"fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":2,"strokeStyle":"solid","roughness":1,"opacity":100,"angle":0,"strokeColor":"#f59e0b","backgroundColor":"transparent","seed":63,"groupIds":[],"frameId":null,"boundElements":null,"updated":1,"link":null,"locked":false},
    {"type":"text","id":"p6-items","x":80,"y":1598,"width":750,"height":210,"text":"1. Build membership base (200-400 members = $20-80K/mo recurring revenue)\n2. Add high-revenue services (body contouring $2-5K, PRP $800-1,200, laser $1.5-3K)\n3. Hire additional providers (2-4 injectors/estheticians to increase capacity)\n4. Retail skincare sales (30-40% margins, $5-15K/mo additional revenue)\n5. Package & bundle strategy (buy 3 get 1 free syringe, annual Botox plans)\n6. Weight loss program (Semaglutide/Tirzepatide $399-599/mo — HUGE demand right now)\n7. Loyalty program (points system — drives repeat visits & referrals)\n8. Second location planning (once first location at 80%+ capacity)","fontSize":16,"fontFamily":1,"textAlign":"left","verticalAlign":"top","containerId":null,"originalText":"1. Build membership base (200-400 members = $20-80K/mo recurring revenue)\n2. Add high-revenue services (body contouring $2-5K, PRP $800-1,200, laser $1.5-3K)\n3. Hire additional providers (2-4 injectors/estheticians to increase capacity)\n4. Retail skincare sales (30-40% margins, $5-15K/mo additional revenue)\n5. Package & bundle strategy (buy 3 get 1 free syringe, annual Botox plans)\n6. Weight loss program (Semaglutide/Tirzepatide $399-599/mo — HUGE demand right now)\n7. Loyalty program (points system — drives repeat visits & referrals)\n8. Second location planning (once first location at 80%+ capacity)","autoResize":true,"lineHeight":1.25,"versionNonce":0,"isDeleted":false,"fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":2,"strokeStyle":"solid","roughness":1,"opacity":85,"angle":0,"strokeColor":"#1e1e1e","backgroundColor":"transparent","seed":64,"groupIds":[],"frameId":null,"boundElements":null,"updated":1,"link":null,"locked":false},

